Covert Skins.name: AK-47 | Leet Museo
Covert Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a Cubism depiction of Elite Crew Ts sneaking up A-long on Dust II.

Covert Skins.name: Desert Eagle | Ocean Drive
Covert Skins.desc: It has been custom painted using oversaturated colors and different shapes.
Covert Skins.lore: Can't miss—both the colors and when using the weapon

Classified Skins.name: MAC-10 | Toybox
Classified Skins.desc: This custom paint job features brightly-colored drawings of chickens, aliens, defusers and more.

Classified Skins.name: Glock-18 | Snack Attack
Classified Skins.desc: It has been custom painted to resemble junk food trinkets suspended in resin.

Classified Skins.name: SSG 08 | Turbo Peek
Classified Skins.desc: Sports cars race down the side of this custom painted, neon-colored sniper rifle.
Classified Skins.lore: Drifting is a right not a privilege

Restricted Skins.name: MP9 | Mount Fuji
Restricted Skins.desc: An acrylic painting of Mount Fuji at dawn has been applied. The painting is used as a pattern, so each weapon may appear different.

Restricted Skins.name: M4A4 | Spider Lily
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a dark blue base and red spider lilies above the magazine and trigger.
Restricted Skins.lore: Bright colors are a warning, not an invitation

Restricted Skins.name: Five-SeveN | Boost Protocol
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted using high contrast colors. The robot icon beneath the rear sight matches the art on the slide.

Restricted Skins.name: MAG-7 | BI83 Spectrum
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted to resemble iridescent bismuth crystals.
Restricted Skins.lore: Why are the rarest things the most beautiful?

Restricted Skins.name: FAMAS | ZX Spectron
Restricted Skins.desc: This custom paint job uses gaming PCs of old as inspiration. Its black base has been finished with multicolored accents.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Dual Berettas | Tread
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: Both Berettas have been hand etched using a wave pattern. The slides have been painted gold.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Fine details take the longest, add the most, and are noticed the least

Mil-Spec Skins.name: MP7 | Guerrilla
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: This custom paint job features a green base, black details and a forward-facing monkey.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: The lion was never king of the jungle

Mil-Spec Skins.name: AUG | Plague
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted using dark fantasy and horror as inspiration.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: USP-S | Black Lotus
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a black lotus flower on the slide.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Adds 3 kills during pistol round, then is discarded

Mil-Spec Skins.name: G3SG1 | Keeping Tabs
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted using Danger Zone's tactical map display as inspiration.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: You have all the information you need - Franz Kriegeld, Phoenix Tactician

Mil-Spec Skins.name: XM1014 | Watchdog
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a jade green base and two guardian lions watching either direction. A third lion has been painted beneath the rear sight.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: PP-Bizon | Lumen
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted black with red accents. The magazine has been painted to resemble a flashlight.
